  Become the ultimate Dungeon Master as you bribe, entice and coax your
  heroes through their adventures on a quest to restore your guild to
  its ultimate glory!
  Guild of Dungeoneering is a turn-based dungeon crawler with a twist:
  instead of controlling the hero you build the dungeon around him. 
  Using cards drawn from your Guild decks, you lay down rooms, monsters,
  traps and of course loot! Meanwhile your hero is making his own 
  decisions on where to go and what to fight. But will he be strong 
  enough to take on the dungeon's overlord? In between dungeon runs you
  manage your Guild, building new rooms to attract new classes of
  adventurer and to expand your decks of cards with more powerful items
  and events.
